{"tid":1434130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣反擊戰] 全民文宣戰開始","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T00:27:03.000Z","uid":65072,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba64f03cdb3b4e49ae9e60bdc6d5d1cab7ace49","tid":1434130,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:09.000Z","msg":"香港示威已經走在失敗之路上<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1432756/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1432756/page/6</a><br />\n藍屍日日都有呢啲訊息瘋傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426523/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好成日俾壓力文宣，今次我哋要全民文宣，個個有份<br />\n用人海文宣溝淡對家抺黑<br />\n1.) 大家要入藍絲GROUP，越多越好，最好有埋太空卡，多個ACCOUNT入<br />\n2.) 搵唔到就開身邊親朋藍絲手機，加自己入去<br />\n3.) 叫朋友SHARE GROUP<br />\n<br />\n我哋要多提下和理非藍絲721元朗恐襲<br />\n還擊例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67ihYeh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67ihYeh.png&h=0e2aab30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">收到消息，元朗721白衣黑社會，因為警黑包庇沒拉人，又出來攪事....(後面照跟)<br />\n幾十個福建幫人事，向撳完錢嘅市民擺車馬費回鄉，見啲人局住俾十百幾十佢哋....(後面照跟)</span><br />\n<br />\n要做到藍屍唔知信邊邊，大家都假，收得多，就唔會再理呢啲垃圾信息<br />\n屈示威者收錢POST都可以咁處理，聯絡人相信大家識填邊啲人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">而家係文宣關鍵時刻，每人一分力，一齊分擔下文宣組壓力<br />\n冷氣軍司同埋和理非，係時候一齊反擊啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ef63455c41b269fa2c0b689daceba16a626f924","tid":1434130,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"十連為敬"},{"pid":"afb5bce60a4646237d0d6a3ad09b34e7522056fe","tid":1434130,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2d4ee7761a4cd8994cea45471da36c6bf0a7ea23","tid":1434130,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"搞埋youtube文宣！！！！！！"},{"pid":"c35b4e3b5e089dc3c4